"modem. More infomation can be found at <ulink "
"url=\"https://wiki.ubuntu.com/SettingUpModems\">SettingUpModems</ulink> on "
"the Ubuntu Wiki."
msgstr ""
"Lea este archivo; debería decirle qué chipset tiene su módem. Cuando sepa "
"qué chipset tiene, consulte <ulink url=\"&linmodem;\">&linmodem;</ulink> y "
"siga las instrucciones que se indican para su módem. Para más información, "
"pude consultar <ulink "
"url=\"https://wiki.ubuntu.com/SettingUpModems\">SettingUpModems</ulink> en "
"el wiki de Ubuntu (en inglés)."

#: C/internet.xml:174(title)
msgid "Web browsing"
msgstr "Navegar por la web"

#: C/internet.xml:175(para)
msgid ""
"The powerful and secure <application>Mozilla Firefox</application> web "
"browser is included in Ubuntu. <application>Firefox</application> features "
"tabbed browsing, pop-up blocking, built-in search, and live bookmarks. Also "
"supported are popular plug-ins such as Java, Macromedia Flash, and "
"RealPlayer. <application>Firefox</application> can be launched by clicking "
"&firefox;."
msgstr ""
"Ubuntu incluye <application>Mozilla Firefox</application>, un navegador web "
"potente y seguro. <application>Firefox</application> dispone de navegación "
"por pestañas, bloqueo de pop-ups, búsqueda integrada, y marcadores "
"dinámicos. Además, soporta complementos tan populares como Java, Macromedia "
"Flash y RealPlayer. <application>Firefox</application> se puede lanzar "
"pulsando en &firefox;."

#: C/internet.xml:179(title)
msgid "Viewing Online Audio and Video in Firefox"
msgstr "Reproducir sonido y vídeo en línea desde Firefox"

#: C/internet.xml:180(para)
msgid ""
"To view online audio and video streams in "
"<application>Firefox</application>, you may need to install some plugins. "
"Which plugin you choose to install depends on which media player you prefer "
"(see <xref linkend=\"video\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Para poder reproducir flujos de sonido y vídeo en "
"<application>Firefox</application>, tendrá que instalar algunos "
"complementos. Los complementos que debe instalar dependen del reproductor "
"multimedia que prefiera (vea <xref linkend=\"video\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:182(para)
msgid ""
"For the <application>Totem Gstreamer</application> plugin (the default "
"Ubuntu media player), install the <application>totem-gstreamer-firefox-"
"plugin</application> package from the <quote>Universe</quote> repository "
"(see <xref linkend=\"add-applications\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Para usar el complemento de <application>Totem Gstreamer</application> (el "
"reproductor multimedia predeterminado en Ubuntu), instale el paquete "
"<application>totem-gstreamer-firefox-plugin</application> desde el "
"repositorio <quote>Universe</quote> (vea <xref linkend=\"add-"
"applications\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:183(para)
msgid ""
"For the <application>Totem Xine</application> plugin, install the "
"<application>totem-xine-firefox-plugin</application> package from the "
"<quote>Universe</quote> repository (see <xref linkend=\"add-"
"applications\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Para usar el complemento de <application>Totem Xine</application>, instale "
"el paquete <application>totem-xine-firefox-plugin</application> desde el "
"repositorio <quote>Universe</quote> (vea <xref linkend=\"add-"
"applications\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:184(para)
msgid ""
"For the <application>Mplayer</application> plugin, install the "
"<application>mozilla-mplayer</application> package from the "
"<quote>Multiverse</quote> repository (see <xref linkend=\"add-"
"applications\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Para usar el complemento de <application>Mplayer</application>, instale el "
"paquete <application>mozilla-mplayer</application> desde el repositorio "
"<quote>Multiverse</quote> (vea <xref linkend=\"add-applications\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:185(para)
msgid ""
"The changes will take effect when you close and open "
"<application>Firefox</application>."
msgstr ""
"Los cambios tendrán efecto cuando cierre y abra de nuevo "
"<application>Firefox</application>."

#: C/internet.xml:187(para)
msgid ""
"These steps will install the plugin for <application>Firefox</application>. "
"However, to play some formats, you may need to add some extra codecs (see "
"<xref linkend=\"codecs\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Esos pasos instalarán el complemento para "
"<application>Firefox</application>. Sin embargo, para reproducir algunos "
"formatos, necesitará añadir algunos códecs extras (vea <xref "
"linkend=\"codecs\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:190(title)
msgid "Macromedia Flash for Firefox"
msgstr "Macromedia Flash para Firefox"

#: C/internet.xml:191(para)
msgid "To view flash graphics from the Mozilla Firefox web browser:"
msgstr "Para ver gráficos Flash en el navegador web Mozilla Firefox:"

#: C/internet.xml:194(para)
msgid ""
"Install the <application>flashplugin-nonfree</application> package from the "
"<quote>Multiverse</quote> repository (see <xref linkend=\"add-"
"applications\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Instale el paquete <application>flashplugin-nonfree</application> desde el "
"repositorio <quote>Multiverse</quote> (vea <xref linkend=\"add-"
"applications\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:198(para)
msgid ""
"The plug-in will be available the next time you start "
"<application>Firefox</application>."
msgstr ""
"El complemento estará disponible la próxima vez que inicie "
"<application>Firefox</application>."

